<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - 99Commercial</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #ef4444 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1200 300"><path d="M0,96L48,112C96,128,192,160,288,160C384,160,480,128,576,112C672,96,768,96,864,112C960,128,1056,160,1152,160C1248,160,1344,128,1392,112L1440,96L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></svg>') no-repeat center bottom;
            background-size: cover;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .welcome-text {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .main-heading {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1f2937;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .sub-heading {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .reset-box {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .reset-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background-color: #ef4444;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 36px;
        }
        .reset-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .reset-description {
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .reset-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ef4444;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        }
        .reset-button:hover {
            background-color: #dc2626;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .expiry-notice .icon {
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .expiry-text {
            color: #92400e;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .security-notice .icon {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .security-text {
            color: #991b1b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .account-info {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .account-heading {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .account-details {
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .account-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .account-links a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .support-info {
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .support-info a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #1f2937;
            color: #9ca3af;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: #374151;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 5px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 40px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer-links {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer-links a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .copyright {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .disclaimer {
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .disclaimer a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            .reset-box {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 30px 15px;
            }
            .logo {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            .welcome-text {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">99Commercial</div>
            <div class="welcome-text">Reset Your Password</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="main-heading">Password Reset Request</h1>
            <p class="sub-heading">Secure your account with a new password</p>
            
            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <span class="icon">‚è∞</span>
                <span class="expiry-text">This reset link will expire in 10 minutes</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reset-box">
                <div class="reset-icon">üîê</div>
                <div class="reset-title">Password Reset Required</div>
                <div class="reset-description">
                    Hi {{firstName}},<br><br>
                    We received a request to reset your password for your 99Commercial account. Click the button below to create a new secure password and regain access to your account.
                </div>
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/auth/reset-password?token={{resetToken}}" class="reset-button">Reset My Password</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <span class="icon">üîí</span>
                <span class="security-text">If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="account-info">
                <h3 class="account-heading">Your account information:</h3>
                <div class="account-details">
                    <strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}
                </div>
                <div class="account-details">
                    <strong>Name:</strong> {{firstName}} {{lastName}}
                </div>
                <div class="support-info">
                    For customer support contact <a href="mailto:support@99commercial.com">support@99commercial.com</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-logo">99Commercial</div>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">YouTube</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/subscription">Subscription Centre</a>
            </div>
            <div class="copyright">
                ¬© 2025 99Commercial. All rights reserved.
            </div>
            <div class="disclaimer">
                This email was sent to {{email}} on behalf of 99Commercial. This email is confidential and intended solely for the use of the individual or entity to whom it is addressed. If you have received this email in error, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@99commercial.com">support@99commercial.com</a>.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
